n  |percentage = 100.00\n  |change     = \n}}\n{{Election box end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website |https://www.mattgurtler.com/}} (campaign)\n<!-- GA House members do not get an official website; the closest is http://www.house.ga.gov/Representatives/en-US/member.aspx?Member=4884&Session=25 -->\n\n{{Georgia House of Representatives}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gurtler, Matt}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Georgia (U.S. state) Republicans]]\n[[Category:Members of the Georgia House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:People from Rabun County, Georgia]]\n[[Category:University of North Georgia alumni]]\n[[Category:21st-century American politicians]]\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n", "name_user": "CarterSmith123", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eCareer)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matt_Gurtler"}
